::: {#e756eeb4 .cell execution_count=25}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# Rule 3: stop when zero falls outside the confidence sequence.
fit.confint(
    inference_type="savi",
    mixture_precision=mixture_precision,
).loc["treated"]
```

